                <p>
                  The function <m>f</m> itself has no critical points.
                  Checking the value of <m>f</m> at the corners <m>(1,1)</m>,
                  <m>(-1,1)</m> and the critical point <m>(5/14,25/196)</m>,
                  we find the absolute maximum is at
                  <m>(5/14,25/196,25/28) \approx (0.357,0.128,0.893)</m> and the absolute minimum is at <m>(-1,1,-12)</m>.
                </p>
